(static) getBattery(mac)

Get the BTM battery status.
  • This is an asynchronous call, it will return immediately.
  • If get successfully, following event will be emit:
    BTMModule.Event_Notify("event_notify_btm")
    The key and value will be as below:
    KeyValue
    actionBTMProfileModule.ACTION_BTM_BATTERY("battery_btm")
    BTMProfileModule.BTM_BATTERYValue range: 0 Low power,1 Not Low power
  • If error happens, following event will be emit:
    BTMModule.Event_Notify("event_notify_btm")
    The key and value will be as below:
    KeyValue
    actionBTMProfileModule.ACTION_ERROR_BTM("action_error_btm")
    actionBTMProfileModule.ERROR_NUM_BTM("error_num")
    actionBTMProfileModule.ERROR_DESCRIPTION_BTM("description")
  • Attention, if you want to be notified, it is mandatory to call following method before you call this method:
    DeviceEventEmitter.addListener(BTMModule.Event_Notify, function (e: Event){});
Parameters:
Name Type Description
mac string Device's mac address
Source:
  • BTMModule.js, line 53

(static) getMemoryData(mac)

Get the value of historical data in the BTM.
  • This is an asynchronous call, it will return immediately.
  • If get successfully, following event will be emit:
    BTMModule.Event_Notify("event_notify_btm")
    The key and value will be as below:
    KeyValue
    actionBTMProfileModule.ACTION_BTM_MEMORY("memory_btm")
    BTMProfileModule.MEMORY_COUNT("memory_count")Memory count for BTM device.
    BTMProfileModule.BTM_TEMPERATURE_ARRAY("btm_temperature_array")The key of the temperature array for BTM device
    BTMProfileModule.BTM_TEMPERATURE_TARGET("btm_temperature_target")The key of the temperature target for BTM device.
    BTMProfileModule.BTM_TEMPERATURE("btm_temperature")The key of the temperature for BTM device
    BTMProfileModule.BTM_MEASURE_TIME("measure_time")The key of the time of memory data for BTM device
  • If error happens, following event will be emit:
    BTMModule.Event_Notify("event_notify_btm")
    The key and value will be as below:
    actionBTMProfileModule.ACTION_ERROR_BTM("action_error_btm")
    actionBTMProfileModule.ERROR_NUM_BTM("error_num")
    actionBTMProfileModule.ERROR_DESCRIPTION_BTM("description")
  • Attention, if you want to be notified, it is mandatory to call following method before you call this method:
    DeviceEventEmitter.addListener(BTMModule.Event_Notify, function (e: Event){});

Name Type Description
mac string Device's mac address
